        options.\cf13 addOption\cf11 (\cf12 Option\cf11 .\cf13 builder\cf11 (\cf14 "p"\cf11 )\
            .\cf13 longOpt\cf11 (\cf14 "path"\cf11 )\
            .\cf13 hasArg\cf11 ()\
