\fs40 \cf4 Key Differences\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs28\fsmilli14400 \cf16 \cb17 api
\fs32 \cf4 \cb1  - Exposes to Plugin Users\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0\cf4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Dependencies become part of the plugin's public API\
\ls13\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Available on the classpath of projects using your plugin\
\ls13\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Transitive to plugin consumers\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs28\fsmilli14400 \cf16 \cb17 implementation
\fs32 \cf4 \cb1  - Internal to Plugin\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0\cf4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Dependencies are hidden from plugin users\
\ls14\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Only available inside your plugin code\
\ls14\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Not transitive to plugin consumers\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs40 \cf4 Example\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf8 \cb9 gradle\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf11 \cb9 // In your plugin's build.gradle\
\
dependencies \{\
    // Plugin users CAN see and use this\
    api 'com.example:launcher-api:1.0.0'\
    \
    // Plugin users CANNOT see this\
    implementation 'com.google.code.gson:gson:2.10.1'\
    implementation 'commons-cli:commons-cli:1.6.0'\
    \
    // For compilation only, not bundled\
    compileOnly 'com.example:target-app:1.0.0'\
\}\cb1 \
